{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "64c0e7d96f5bfc7ab78ae85d", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d7713c52ffa3c944600e3"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fed2b295b085ab6eba3"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "61a8bf0fc821b6514e527d7a", "title": "BITSAT 2016", "isVisible": true}], "position": 0, "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 2, "approximateTimeRequired": 90, "question": {"text": "In the Young's double-slit experiment, the intensity of light at a point on the screen where the path difference is $\\lambda$ is $\\mathrm{K},(\\lambda$ being the wave length of light used). The intensity at a point where the path difference is $\\lambda / 4,$ will be :", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "dCzNa", "text": "$\\mathrm{K}$", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}, {"id": "6uoiV", "text": "$\\mathrm{K} / 4$", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}, {"id": "L9IbG", "text": "$\\mathrm{K} / 2$", "isCorrect": true, "image": null}, {"id": "g4xAX", "text": "Zero", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "For path difference $\\lambda,$ phase difference $=2 \\pi \\mathrm{rad}$\r\n\r\nFor path difference $\\frac{\\lambda}{4},$ phase difference\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\n=\\frac{\\pi}{2} \\mathrm{rad}\r\n\r\n$$\r\n\r\nAs $\\mathrm{K}=4 \\mathrm{I}_{0}$ so intensity at given point where\r\n\r\npath difference is $\\frac{\\lambda}{4}$\r\n\r\n$\\mathrm{K}^{\\prime}=4 \\mathrm{I}_{0} \\cos ^{2}\\left(\\frac{\\pi}{4}\\right)\\left(\\cos \\frac{\\pi}{4}=\\cos 45^{\\circ}\\right)$\r\n\r\n$=2 \\mathrm{I}_{0}=\\frac{\\mathrm{K}}{2}$", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "numericalLowerLimit": null, "questionLabels": [], "__v": 0, "masterId": "MOGBSPYQ11171104", "bucket": "", "category": null, "microConcepts": [], "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText